appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New feature: Introducing Customer Service Live Chat.
- Now you can view your business trips booked by your company right within the app.
- Stay informed with SMS and push notifications for any cancellations from DEXTR.
- Resolved an issue where the discount amount on the referral image would disappear after changing the language.
- Fixed a bug where address suggestions were not displayed when entering the full address.
- Address inconsistencies throughout the app have been resolved.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Bug fix: Resolved an issue where the user's LiveChat wasn't being assigned to any group.
Bug fix: Addressed the LiveChat getting stuck in "awaiting agent" status.
Bug fix: Corrected the erroneous password prompt.
Bug fix: Fixed inconsistencies in the 'no show' status update.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What's new in this version?
- Feature: Introducing the ability to add your flight number to ride details for airport trips. Keep your drivers informed and ensure a timely pick-up.
- Bug Fix: We've addressed the issue that caused the app to crash when sharing referral codes. Your referrals should now go smoothly.
- Bug Fix: Fixed an issue with the "Back to Home" button on the booking confirmation page. It will now correctly redirect you to the homepage.
